{"word":"ἐσκάλισις","slug":"ἐσκάλισις","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n42905\" key=\"e)ska/lisis\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἐσκάλισις</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">εως</itype>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen>, prob.<sense id=\"n42905.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">packing in a wooden crate</tr_> (cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κᾶλον</foreign>), <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ IG\">IG</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.1485.85</biblScope> </bibl> (Epid.); cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">παρκάλισις</foreign> and perh. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">διακάλισις,</foreign> unless all three words belong to <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">καλινδέω</foreign> (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">καλίω</etym>).</sense> </entryFree>"}]}